	(6,'I think this would work better if there was a widget or something that could be downloaded that worked alongside the site (integration). If I open another tab, I don\'t get voice notifications from Pomodoro Crate, and I have to keep an eye on when I finish, or I will never know that my 25 minutes is up. I really like the task list feature, but the timer itself caused too many problems for me, especially since I wasn\'t being notified at the end, nor does the timer go automatically into a break if there are remaining pomodoros to complete (which means I end up taking a bit of a break before I ever start counting down my 5 minute break). It just wasn\'t efficient enough for me, but the website looks amazing, and you\'ve done a great job with it so far. If you can work out details about the timer itself and maybe integrate a desktop widget, this would be the perfect task management system. Good luck, and thanks for the invitation to the site.',0,0,1,19,'2011-03-20 23:34:28','2011-03-20 23:34:28','<code class=\'debug_dump\'>{\"SERVER_SOFTWARE\"=>\"Apache/2.2.3 (CentOS)\", \"SERVER_PROTOCOL\"=>\"HTTP/1.1\", \"SERVER_NAME\"=>\"pomodorocrate.com\", \"SERVER_ADMIN\"=>\"tech@easymedia.ro\", \"SERVER_ADDR\"=>\"195.216.222.67\", \"SERVER_PORT\"=>\"80\", \"REMOTE_ADDR\"=>\"98.80.190.54\", \"REMOTE_PORT\"=>\"51941\", \"REQUEST_METHOD\"=>\"GET\", \"QUERY_STRING\"=>\"\", \"DOCUMENT_ROOT\"=>\"/var/www/vhosts/pomodorocrate.com/rails/pomodorocrate/current/public/\", \"REQUEST_URI\"=>\"/contact_requests/new\", \"SCRIPT_NAME\"=>\"\", \"PATH_INFO\"=>\"/contact_requests/new\", \"HTTP_HOST\"=>\"pomodorocrate.com\", \"HTTP_USER_AGENT\"=>\"Mozilla/5.0 (Macintosh; U; Intel Mac OS X 10_6_6; en-us) AppleWebKit/533.20.25 (KHTML, like Gecko) Version/5.0.4 Safari/533.20.27\", \"HTTP_ACCEPT\"=>\"application/xml,application/xhtml+xml,text/html;q=0.9,text/plain;q=0.8,image/png,*/*;q=0.5\", \"HTTP_REFERER\"=>\"http://pomodorocrate.com/activities\", \"HTTP_ACCEPT_LANGUAGE\"=>\"en-us\", \"HTTP_ACC